, male. 4a, right mandible, ventral view. 4b, left mandible, ventral view. 4c, right mandible, ventral view and detail of mola, scanning microscope image. 4d, left mandible, ventral view and detail of mola, scanning microscope image. 4e, maxilla, ventral view. 4f, maxilla, detail of palpus, lascinia and galea, ventral view. 4g, labium, ventral view.
</paragraph>
